fields.description:
When a TextField is used inside a TableView, its selection position (cursor) gets reset when
a resize of the TableView occurs (ex: orientation change, keyboard appears/disappears).

{code}

var win = Ti.UI.createWindow();

var tableView = Ti.UI.createTableView();
win.add(tableView);

var tableRow = Ti.UI.createTableViewRow();
tableRow.add(Ti.UI.createTextField({width: '100%'}));
tableView.appendRow(tableRow);

win.open();
{code}

1. Run this application.
2. Focus the textfield and type some text.
3. Hide the keyboard OR rotate screen to trigger orientation change.

Expected: selection position in textfield should be the same.
Actual: selection position is reset to 0 (start).
